<li>
<p>AI systems often deal with <strong>incomplete, uncertain, or noisy data<=
/strong>.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Probabilistic reasoning allows AI to <strong>quantify uncertainty</stron=
g> and <strong>make rational decisions</strong>.</p></li>
</ul>
