eatures + Labels) =E2=86=92 Train Model =E2=86=92 Evaluate =E2=86=92 Predic=
t
</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p><strong>Common Algorithms:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"62=
c9aeab-911e-4814-8d0a-7dc2bfd4d267" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Algorithm</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Description</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Example</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Linear Regression</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Predicts continuous values</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>House prices</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Logistic Regression</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Predicts probability of a class</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Email spam detection</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Decision Tree</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Tree-based model for classification/regression</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Loan approval</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Support Vector Machine (SVM)</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Separates classes using hyperplane</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Image classification</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Neural Networks</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Complex mapping from input to output</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Handwriting recognition</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p><strong>Applications:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Email spam detection</p></li>
<li>
<p>Credit scoring</p></li>
<li>
<p>Stock price prediction</p></li>
<li>
<p>Medical diagnosis</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 id=3D"ArtificialIntelligence-3=EF=B8=8F=E2=83=A3UnsupervisedLearning(Cl=
ustering)"><strong>3=EF=B8=8F=E2=83=A3 Unsupervised Learning (Clustering)</=
strong></h2>
<p><strong>Definition:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Learns patterns from <strong>unlabeled data</strong>.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Goal: <strong>Group similar data points</strong> together (discover hidd=
en structure).</p></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Key Concept: Clustering</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Partition data into <strong>clusters</strong> such that points in the sa=
me cluster are similar.</p></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Common Algorithms:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"22=
3f51ea-7b86-4e07-bbf6-9f72d8e46476" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Algorithm</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Description</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Example</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>K-Means</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Partitions data into K clusters based on distance</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Customer segmentation</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Hierarchical Clustering</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Builds a tree of clusters (dendrogram)</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Document clustering</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>DBSCAN</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Density-based clustering, handles noise</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Geospatial data analysis</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Gaussian Mixture Model (GMM)</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Probabilistic clustering</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Image segmentation</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p><strong>Applications:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Market segmentation</p></li>
<li>
<p>Anomaly detection (fraud detection)</p></li>
<li>
<p>Document or text clustering</p></li>
<li>
<p>Image segmentation</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 id=3D"ArtificialIntelligence-4=EF=B8=8F=E2=83=A3KeyDifferences:Supervis=
edvsUnsupervised"><strong>4=EF=B8=8F=E2=83=A3 Key Differences: Supervised v=
s Unsupervised</strong></h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"f7=
f24cbf-dc74-4ed1-83ea-1e1a83c4ac67" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Feature</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Supervised Learning</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Unsupervised Learning (Clustering)</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Data</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Labeled</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Unlabeled</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Goal</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Predict labels</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Find patterns/structure</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Feedback</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Uses known output for training</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>No feedback, discovers hidden patterns</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Algorithms</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Regression, Classification (Decision Trees, SVM)</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>K-Means, Hierarchical, DBSCAN</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Applications</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Spam detection, medical diagnosis</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Market segmentation, anomaly detection</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"ArtificialIntelligence-=E2=9C=85Summary.8">=E2=9C=85 <strong>Summ=
ary</strong></h3>
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>Supervised Learning:</strong> Uses labeled data to <strong>predi=
ct outputs</strong>; includes regression and classification algorithms.</p>=
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Unsupervised Learning (Clustering):</strong> Uses unlabeled data=
 to <strong>discover structure</strong>; includes K-Means, Hierarchical, DB=
SCAN.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Both are <strong>foundational in AI and data analysis</strong>, but diff=
er in <strong>data type and goals</strong>.</p></li>
</ul>
