<h3 id=3D"ArtificialIntelligence-=E2=9C=85Summary.10">=E2=9C=85 <strong>Sum=
mary</strong></h3>
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>Regression</strong> predicts <strong>continuous outcomes</strong=
> based on input features.</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Types:</strong> Linear, Polynomial, Logistic, Ridge, Lasso, Elas=
tic Net</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Goal:</strong> Model the relationship and <strong>minimize predi=
ction error</strong>.</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Applications:</strong> Finance, healthcare, weather, sales, real=
 estate</p></li>
</ul>
